  <verse number="9" style="v" />But avoid foolish debates and genealogies and strife and conflict about the law. Those things are worthless and unprofitable.

  <verse number="10" style="v" />Reject anyone who is causing divisions among you, after one or two warnings,

  <verse number="11" style="v" />and know that such a one has turned from the right way and is sinning and condemns himself.</para>
